This tool is developed for internal use within IBM to facilitate the installation
and management of AI skills for IBM Bob (enterprise AI coding assistant).

INTERNAL USE ONLY - NOT FOR EXTERNAL DISTRIBUTION

This installer is provided as-is for use by IBM employees and authorized personnel
to enhance their development workflows with IBM Bob.

